ee.sk.digidoc
Class KeyInfo

java.lang.Object
  ee.sk.digidoc.KeyInfo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class KeyInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Models the KeyInfo block of an XML-DSIG signature. In DigiDoc library the key info allways contains only one subject certificate, e.g. no uplinks and the smaller items like RSA public key modulus and export are not kept separately but calculated online from the signers certificate. That means they are read-only attributes.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Veiko Sinivee
